title: Orebfuscator插件无法加载
author: hua2hua
txt_content:
[10:32:56 警告] Skipping loading of Orebfuscator as it does not work with Spigot 1.8 builds!我下载的是1.7.2的
spigot-1.7.10-SNAPSHOT-b1657

replies.author: Mr.柴
replies.txt_content: 估计是核心问题 识别你核心是 Spigot 1.8 builds

replies.txt_content: 版本不兼容 更换适合版本
